summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4911 for the improvement of The South 210-feet of alley, Block 8, Squire's Lakeside Addition, being the alley between Rainier Avenue and 36th Avenue South, from Dakota Street north; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 56272, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
